   │
 4 │     lda #TASKS          // ERR: var is not a numeric value, use &&TASKS instead
   │          ──┬──  
   │            ╰──── var reference
   │ 
   │ Help: use `&&TASKS` to load its 16-bit address, or `&&&TASKS` for the far address
